text:
From start to finish my experience with Yaniv & Associates was quick, painless, professional, helpful, and not clinical.
Everyone who helped me was really nice over email, divorce was quick, painless and went through extremely fast (it was expedited).
I would recommend them to anyone! I'm glad I found them!
